022/10/FfO7-voacAEZXTh.jpeg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/FfO7-voacAEZXTh.jpeg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/FfO7-voacAEZXTh.jpeg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.48.12-PM-1.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.47.30-PM-1.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/FfO8bJcaMAE6IfD.jpeg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.48.12-PM-1.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-19-at-5.44.06-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.58.46-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-19-at-5.44.06-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/FfO8bJcaMAE6IfD.jpeg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/FfO7-voacAEZXTh.jpeg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-21-at-11.44.52-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.58.46-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-19-at-5.44.06-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.47.53-PM-1.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.47.53-PM-1.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-1.07.39-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.55.00-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-21-at-11.44.52-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.55.00-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-24-at-10.49.20-AM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-1.07.39-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/FfO7PYVaAAATIyD.jpeg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-21-at-11.44.52-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.58.46-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/FfO5BFuaYAIQfVf.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.47.30-PM-1.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.48.12-PM-1.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.48.12-PM-1.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-21-at-11.44.52-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-1.04.18-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.55.00-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-24-at-10.49.20-AM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-1.04.18-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/FfO7PYVaAAATIyD.jpeg"], "content": "<p>The Line is a micro-verse to connect thousands of artists together in a single line filled with 1 million artworks. <strong>Yes... 1 million artworks. </strong></p><p>One million is not an impossible goal if 3 - 4,000 artists add their collections to The Line. Already over 10,000 artworks have been added by the first 151 artists. </p><p>As we get closer to our goal, we will invite CNN's viewers in and say 'here, we made this.'</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/theline\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Visit --- The Line ---</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-full kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-21-at-11.44.52-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"804\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-21-at-11.44.52-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-21-at-11.44.52-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-21-at-11.44.52-PM.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-21-at-11.44.52-PM.png 2400w\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/line17\">The Line [17] Minimals by Vivianegbr</a></figcaption></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://forms.gle/3X6mDA66Ehht29MY7\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Artists Join --The Line---</a></div><h2 id=\"the-line\">The Line</h2><p>The Line is a fundamentally new way to experience art in a 3d space. It removes many of the barriers that made it more difficult than 2d environments most web users are accustomed too. It also solves many problems for artists and collectors.</p><p>1) <strong>Browsing art in The Line is effortless.</strong> <em>No portals blocking art.</em><br />2) <strong>Navigating in The Line is easy. </strong><em>Two directions. Forward and back.</em><br />3) <strong>Big Screen artworks in The Line. </strong><em>No artificial walls restricting art size. </em></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-wide\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-24-at-10.49.20-AM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1001\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-24-at-10.49.20-AM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-24-at-10.49.20-AM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-24-at-10.49.20-AM.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-24-at-10.49.20-AM.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px\"></figure><h2 id=\"why-the-line-is-needed\">Why The Line is needed</h2><p>It is time to get back to the art. The art is what sustains the culture of Web3.0. It is the very bedrock and foundational layer. You can read the whole tweet-thread below.</p><p>We are each a mere dot in this new metaverse world we are buidling. Together we become The Line.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/FfO5BFuaYAIQfVf.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1034\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/FfO5BFuaYAIQfVf.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/FfO5BFuaYAIQfVf.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/FfO5BFuaYAIQfVf.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/FfO5BFuaYAIQfVf.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>The moment I first saw something like the Metaverse... ....Neo was introduced to the construct in The Matrix.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/FfO7EEoaMAEAzZ7.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"976\" height=\"549\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/FfO7EEoaMAEAzZ7.jpeg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/FfO7EEoaMAEAzZ7.jpeg 976w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>The ability to experience everything conjured up from white space felt freeing.</p><p>Yet early Metaverse worlds are suffering three problems. </p><p>1) They feel like kids games... <br />2) Are hard to navigate...or <br />3) Art is locked behind slow loading doors.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/FfO7PYVaAAATIyD.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1272\" height=\"1170\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/FfO7PYVaAAATIyD.jpeg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/FfO7PYVaAAATIyD.jpeg 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/FfO7PYVaAAATIyD.jpeg 1272w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>The Line fixes this. Walk forward. Return again. Experience way more art without portals getting in the way.</p><p></p><p>The Line is for artists to showcase 100+ artwork collections with clarity.</p><blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\">\"Excited to be part of this epic project.\" <a href=\"https://twitter.com/briancattelle\">@briancattelle</a></blockquote><p>No distractions. No fuss. No skeumorphic virtual timber beams weighing heavily on your art. It is time to get back to the art.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/FfO7-voacAEZXTh.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"964\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/FfO7-voacAEZXTh.jpeg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/FfO7-voacAEZXTh.jpeg 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/FfO7-voacAEZXTh.jpeg 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/FfO7-voacAEZXTh.jpeg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>At the end of The Line is a portal. The portal connects you to the next artist in The Line.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/FfO8bJcaMAE6IfD.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1095\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/FfO8bJcaMAE6IfD.jpeg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/FfO8bJcaMAE6IfD.jpeg 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/FfO8bJcaMAE6IfD.jpeg 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/FfO8bJcaMAE6IfD.jpeg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>Nokia snake game fans will be able to connect the dots... ...with what we are attempting to buidl here.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/nokia-snake.gif\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"338\" height=\"350\"></figure><p>If we each connect our curated part of the Metaverse together... ...The Line could become quite a substantial experience.</p><blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\">Thank you!  love the concept so much!! @spydenator</blockquote><p>Major alpha alert for collectooors. You will be able to experience all of an artists collections.... ...by simply walking The Line. </p><blockquote class=\"kg-blockquote-alt\">\"Love this Line\" <a href=\"https://twitter.com/parachicaa\">@parachicaa</a></blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1ET8S2C4DWc?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"a\nccelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen title=\"The Line\"></iframe></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-full\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-19-at-5.44.06-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"756\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-19-at-5.44.06-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-19-at-5.44.06-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-19-at-5.44.06-PM.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-19-at-5.44.06-PM.png 2400w\"></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">🌟 Massive ups to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@mintfaced</a> for creating the cool Line concept - a collaborative art galleries project on a massive scale.<br /><br />Just started creating my line  (118) Link below.<br />One side is the SR Species graphic novel and the other - all SR artworks.<br /><br />LFG! <a href=\"https://t.co/sK84xe3Uce\">https://t.co/sK84xe3Uce</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/jw2F5quN4w\">pic.twitter.com/jw2F5quN4w</a></p>&mdash; 🔥Deconstruct 💎 Now on SuperRare (@spydenator) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/spydenator/status/1584751160459608065?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 25, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p>For casual art enjoyooors... ....the next portal always awaits. </p><p>We are more than our TradArt classifications, country of origin nations or Foundation rankings.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">The Line is a Monumental new art project by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@mintfaced</a><br />Top tier Artists all in line showcasing work, Please take a walk around and look at my art, featuring my Photography, Digital Art, and Sketches. Then walk through doors to the other galleries as well! <a href=\"https://t.co/Kn3tobkdeT\">https://t.co/Kn3tobkdeT</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/Oz91cr0oQC\">pic.twitter.com/Oz91cr0oQC</a></p>&mdash; whatIF | sauCnft | ph0t0s.eth (@sauCnft) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/sauCnft/status/1584739983193034753?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 25, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">It is time to get back to the art.<br /><br />Introducing The Line.<br /><br />1/30 <a href=\"https://t.co/COz8g1elrJ\">pic.twitter.com/COz8g1elrJ</a></p>&mdash; MintFace 🍒 (@mintfaced) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1581813211271426048?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 17, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-full kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-18-at-9.21.33-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1181\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-18-at-9.21.33-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-18-at-9.21.33-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-18-at-9.21.33-PM.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-18-at-9.21.33-PM.png 2076w\"><figcaption>Shawn Moreton's Ice Shacks on <a href=\"https://oncyber.io/line8\">The Line [8]</a></figcaption></figure><h2 id=\"visit-the-line\">Visit The Line</h2><p>You can explore The Line from the begining or go directly to a part of The Line you choose.</p><p><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/theline\">oncyber.io/theline</a><br /><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/line1\">oncyber.io/line1</a><br /><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/line2\">oncyber.io/line2</a><br />...<br /><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/line69\">oncyber.io/line69</a><br />...<br /><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/line100\">oncyber.io/line100</a></p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/theline\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Visit --- The Line ---</a></div><h2 id=\"artists-join-the-line\">Artists Join The Line</h2><p>You can join The Line if you have minted artworks to share. The rules are simple on The Line:</p><p>❤️ Only add art you have created <br />💀No memes or pfps.</p><p>That's it! </p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://forms.gle/3X6mDA66Ehht29MY7\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Artists Join --- The Line ---</a></div><p>Our commitment to you is your application will be processed quickly. Usually the same day. No waiting for weeks without hearing anything... we are not TradArt 😂</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-full kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-19-at-5.36.20-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1043\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-19-at-5.36.20-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-19-at-5.36.20-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-19-at-5.36.20-PM.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-19-at-5.36.20-PM.png 2282w\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/line30\">@Thompsonnft at The Line [30]</a></figcaption></figure><h2 id=\"become-a-patron-of-the-line\">Become A Patron of The Line</h2><p>By becoming a Patron of The Line, you are contributing to resources needed to extend The Line to support thousands of artists and up to 1 million artworks. </p><p>There are three Patron of The Line tiers to choose from with benefits including <em>a feature Patron plaque on up to 500 segments of The Line,</em> access to display your own collection of art on an exclusive <em>Patron Collectors</em> section of The Line and being listed on <em>The Line Exclusive list </em>for artists on The Line to reward<em>.</em></p><p></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.47.30-PM-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1922\" height=\"548\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.47.30-PM-1.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.47.30-PM-1.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.47.30-PM-1.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.47.30-PM-1.png 1922w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h3 id=\"topline-patron\">TopLine Patron</h3><p>The TopLine Patron shows visitors throughout The Line that the holder is a significant contributor to the Web3.0 art scene. Benefits including the following:</p><p><strong>TopLine Patron Benefits</strong><br />1. The <strong>TopLine Patron</strong> receives a personalised minted plaque showing the patrons name and pfp in up to 500 segments of The Line.<br />2. The <strong>TopLine Patron </strong>gets to nominate 3x wallet addresses of their choosing to put on <em>The Line Exclusive</em> artist list for free airdrops and allowlists as decided by artists anywhere along The Line.<br />3. <strong>The TopLine Patron</strong> receives 3x <em>Patron Collectors section</em> of The Line to display any artwork they like to visitors of The Line.</\np><p>Exclusivity: 5 Patrons<br />Price: 10 eth <br />Duration: 12 months renewable</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x269bc803c233620506c9d25d980e979bf8bcbbf6/2\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Become A TopLine Patron</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x269bc803c233620506c9d25d980e979bf8bcbbf6/2\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.55.00-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1858\" height=\"1196\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.55.00-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.55.00-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.55.00-PM.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.55.00-PM.png 1858w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><hr /><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.47.53-PM-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1976\" height=\"618\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.47.53-PM-1.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.47.53-PM-1.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.47.53-PM-1.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.47.53-PM-1.png 1976w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h3 id=\"hardline-patron\">HardLine Patron</h3><p>The <strong>HardLine Patron</strong> demonstrates your commitment as a collector to artists in Web3.0.  </p><p><strong>HardLine Patron Benefits</strong><br />1. The <strong>HardLine Patron</strong> receives a personalised minted plaque showing the patrons name and pfp in up to <em>100 segments</em> of The Line.<br />2. The <strong>HardLine Patron </strong>gets to nominate <em>1x wallet address</em> of their choosing put on <em>The Line Exclusive</em> for free airdrops and allowlists as decided by artists anywhere along The Line.<br />3. <strong>The HardLine Patron</strong> receives 1x <em>Patron Collectors section</em> of The Line to display any artwork they like to visitors of The Line.</p><p>Exclusivity: 10 Patrons<br />Price: 1 eth <br />Duration: 12 months renewable</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x269bc803c233620506c9d25d980e979bf8bcbbf6/3\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Become A HardLine Patron</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x269bc803c233620506c9d25d980e979bf8bcbbf6/3\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.58.46-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1862\" height=\"1060\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.58.46-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.58.46-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.58.46-PM.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.58.46-PM.png 1862w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><hr /><p>Each year, you have the right to renew the patronage with HardLine and TopLine tiers.</p><p></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.48.12-PM-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"690\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.48.12-PM-1.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.48.12-PM-1.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.48.12-PM-1.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-12.48.12-PM-1.png 2040w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h3 id=\"underline-patron\">UnderLine Patron</h3><p>The UnderLine Patron shows both collectors and artists that you are an active member of the art scene and have contributed to buidling of The Line by acquiring an <em>UnderLine Patron</em> NFT. </p><p>An <em>UnderLine Patron </em>NFT as shown below will be displayed on a segment of The Line as a representation of all UnderLine Patron's contribution.<br />Exclusivity: 1,000 Patrons<br />Price: 0.0457<br />Duration: 12 months renewable</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-1.04.18-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1692\" height=\"1500\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-1.04.18-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-1.04.18-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-1.04.18-PM.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-1.04.18-PM.png 1692w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h3 id=\"launch-timing-of-patron-tiers\">Launch Timing of Patron Tiers</h3><p>The <strong>HardLine</strong> <strong>Patron </strong>and <strong>TopLine Patron</strong> Tiers are available now</p><p>Once the allocation have been fully taken up, the <strong>UnderLine Patron</strong> Tier will be opened. This ensures that <strong>HardLine Patrons</strong> and <strong>TopLine Patrons</strong> get first priority on access to benefits.</p><p></p><h3 id=\"how-patron-funds-will-be-allocated\">How Patron Funds Will Be Allocated</h3><p>Patron Funds will be allocated to support three buidl aspects of The Line on its way to displaying 1 million artworks in a single Line.</p><p>1) One then two staff members to support the extension, curation and administration of The Line. Primary activity is onboarding the next 3,000 - 4,000 artists and 1 million artworks in the next 12 months.<br />2) Allocation for OnCyber who is the underlying technology provider for The Line.<br />3) Connectivity and development of The Line space alongside metaverse worlds supportive of art.<br />4) Fund putting The Line on-chain to ensure its long term access as a public good for artists.</p><p>Purchase of each Patron of The Line NFT funds the hardware wallet ourline.eth, managed by mintface.eth. Funds from ourline.eth will be distributed as required to fund 1 - 4 above + gas fees.</p><hr /><h3 id=\"official-links\">Official Links</h3><p><a href=\"https://oncyber.io/theline\">View artists on The Line</a></p><p><a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/wearetheline\">View Patron of The Arts NFTs on OpenSea</a></p><p><a href=\"https://etherscan.io/address/0x269bc803c233620506c9d25d980e979bf8bcbbf6\">View The Line contract on Manifold</a></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><a href=\"https://etherscan.io/address/0x269bc803c233620506c9d25d980e979bf8bcbbf6\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-1.07.39-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"796\" height=\"928\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-1.07.39-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-29-at-1.07.39-PM.png 796w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a><figcaption><a href=\"https://etherscan.io/address/0x269bc8\n03c233620506c9d25d980e979bf8bcbbf6\">View The Line contract on Manifold</a></figcaption></figure><p></p><hr /><h3 id=\"what-artists-are-saying-about-the-line\">What Artists Are Saying About The Line</h3><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">I´m part of &quot;The Line&quot;, an initiative from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@mintfaced</a> 😍<br /><br />&quot;The Line is a place that puts art first. Your art. Your wall.&quot;<br /><br />Link 👇 <a href=\"https://t.co/9rZIanT8Hk\">pic.twitter.com/9rZIanT8Hk</a></p>&mdash; IKERTJE.COM 💎 𝐒𝐑 debut tomorrow, Tuesday! 🚀 (@IkertjeNFT) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/IkertjeNFT/status/1584652201880088576?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 24, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"